# 🎬 My Favorite Movies

Welcome to my collection of favorite films — across Tamil and Hindi cinema. ❤️🎞️

---

## 🇮🇳 Tamil Cinema

### 🧨 Master (2021)
![Master Poster](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/3/36/Master_2021_poster.jpg)
- **Review**: A stylish action-packed entertainer with Thalapathy Vijay in top form and Vijay Sethupathi as a memorable villain.
- **Rating**: ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️ (7/10)

### 🧠 Thani Oruvan (2015)
![Thani Oruvan Poster](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/7/7b/Thani_Oruvan.jpg)
- **Review**: A gripping cat-and-mouse game between a righteous cop and a brilliant villain.
- **Rating**: ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️ (9/10)

### 🌌 Vaaranam Aayiram (2008)
![Vaaranam Aayiram Poster](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/5/54/Vaaranam_Aayiram.jpg)
- **Review**: An emotional journey of love, loss, and personal growth — one of Suriya’s finest performances.
- **Rating**: ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️ (8/10)

### 🎶 Vinnaithaandi Varuvaaya (2010)
![VTV Poster](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/f/f7/Vinnaithaandi_Varuvaayaa_poster.jpg)
- **Review**: A heart-wrenching love story with timeless music and strong emotions.
- **Rating**: ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️ (9/10)

---

## 🇮🇳 Hindi Cinema

### 🎸 Rockstar (2011)
![Rockstar Poster](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/6/6e/Rockstar_%282011_film%29_poster.jpg)
- **Review**: A soul-stirring journey of love, pain, and music; Ranbir Kapoor’s breakout performance.
- **Rating**: ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️ (9/10)

### 🌀 Tamasha (2015)
![Tamasha Poster](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/6/60/Tamasha_Poster.jpg)
- **Review**: A bold take on identity and self-expression with beautiful storytelling.
- **Rating**: ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️ (10/10)

### 🧑‍🎓 Wake Up Sid (2009)
![Wake Up Sid Poster](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/7/74/Wake_Up_Sid.jpg)
- **Review**: A coming-of-age tale that perfectly captures youthful aimlessness and growth.
- **Rating**: ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️ (8/10)

### 💞 Kuch Kuch Hota Hai (1998)
![KKHH Poster](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/d/dd/Kuch_Kuch_Hota_Hai_poster.jpg)
- **Review**: Classic '90s Bollywood magic — friendship, love, and iconic moments.
- **Rating**: ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️ (8/10)

### 🎵 Aashiqui 2 (2013)
![Aashiqui 2 Poster](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/d/da/Aashiqui2poster.jpg)
- **Review**: A tragic love story elevated by its unforgettable soundtrack.
- **Rating**: ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️ (8/10)

### 👨‍👩‍👦 Kabhi Khushi Kabhie Gham (2001)
![K3G Poster](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/c/cd/Kabhi_Khushi_Kabhie_Gham_poster.jpg)
- **Review**: Family drama, emotions, and grandeur — a true Karan Johar spectacle.
- **Rating**: ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️ (7/10)

